snippet.title: Stanford Rapist Gets Short Jail Sentence Because Jail Might Be Hard For Him
snippet.description:
The Stanford rapist gets only a 6 month jail sentence because jail would have a "severe impact" on him. 

Watch our original video: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ai_07ktDd3Q

Survivor's full letter: https://www.buzzfeed.com/katiejmbaker/heres-the-powerful-letter-the-stanford-victim-read-to-her-ra?utm_term=.ta43gWWR2y#.veP0rJJgMv
